task_text: Do we have an office in Wien (Yes/No)

text_blocks:
Based on the company context I have, Bellini Industria Vernici S.p.A. has offices in:
- Italy HQ (between Milan/Bergamo)
- Serbia (Novi Sad)
- Munich, Germany
- Paris, France
- Rotterdam, Netherlands
- Barcelona, Spain
- Vienna, Austria

"Wien" is the German name for Vienna, Austria. Yes, the company has an office in Vienna.
